main event: A UFO observation was reported on November 21, 1967, in Milton, Wisconsin, but deemed to have insufficient data for further investigation.
interesting points: The observer requested reporting forms to provide more information but did not return them,The report was generated by the Air Force's Foreign Technology Division,The document does not include any physical evidence or photographs,The conclusion of the report stated 'INSUFFICIENT DATA',An additional mention of a sighting by Bayfield County Sheriff's Office personnel was noted on the same morning.
